It can be both author's works in which your creative abilities will be shown and training materials related to the work with exchange’ functionality. And now the main thing! Awards to winners in both categories will be distributed as follows: 1st place - $ 1000 in the equivalent of deex tokens. 2nd place - $ 700 in the equivalent of deex tokens. 3rd place - $ 500 in the equivalent of deex tokens. 4th place - $ 300 in the equivalent of deex tokens.   5th place - $ 100 in the equivalent of deex tokens. Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: We are opening a new gateway for the replenishment of the exchange accounts using Zcash digital asset. Zcash is a decentralized and open-source cryptocurrency that sets a new standard for privacy and anonymity through the use of unique methods of cryptography. Zcash level of anonymity was noted by many well-known companies and individuals. For example, WikiLeaks began accepting donations in Zcash, as Edward Snowden has called this the best cryptocurrency alternative to Bitcoin. Recently anonymous coins have been delisted from many trading platforms. Following the basic principles of decentralization for the work of the Zcash for gateway we have implemented anonymous z-addresses, while most of the public addresses have "t" index. The gateway is currently working only for replenishment, in the near future withdrawal for this asset will be released. Body: Dear friends and partners!  We are pleased to announce that today the list of tokens available for trading has been replenished. Another asset available for financial transactions on the DEEX exchange has become the STASIS EURS (EURS) asset.  https://stasis.net/  The STASIS team has developed EURS specifically to meet the growing demand for cryptocurrency from European institutional investors.  By investing in EURS, investors have access to a reliable product during periods of excessive volatility and speculation in the cryptocurrency markets, combined with the additional ability to freely transfer assets off-network to the blockchain and back. Investors achieve this with sharply reduced counterparty risk as a result of a transparent and vertically integrated network of platform partners led by European broker - Exante.  The gateway for STASIS asset works only for replenishment. The minimum amount is 10 and the maximum is 100 EUR. After carrying out all the necessary tests, the withdraw will also be available.

Author: pringles1901
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: We have updated the exchange functionality of https://alpha.deex.exchange/. The next update of the current version includes a number of important fixes.  A full list is provided below. 1. Added Trading view graphics and tools. 2. BTC withdraw is available. 3. Added the ability to full logout. 4. Faster and more optimized search for "Send" and "Find markets" interfaces. 5. Improved layout in Firefox. 6. Improved exchange interface, optimized empty space. 7. Small fixes and improvements in the dark theme. 8. Small corrections of the General layout.  As always, we are waiting for your comments and suggestions and will soon be ready to present a beta version of the exchange.  Along with the release of the update, we are pleased to announce the listing of Bitcoen and EXenium projects tokens.  Bitcoen is a peer-to-peer payment system that uses the same settlement unit. Cryptographic methods are used to ensure the functioning and protection of the system. All information about transactions between addresses of the system is available. The project website is http://bitcoen.io/  EXenium is a cryptocurrency trading platform, implemented in the form of chat bot for most popular instant messengers. With its user-friendly interface and ease to use functionality, the platform is popular within cryptocurrency enthusiasts around the world. The project website is https://exenium.net/. In the near future the mutual listing of DEEX token on EXenium will be done.  Cooperation with centralized exchanges is becoming a good tradition. The results of cooperation are mutual listings, actions, PR and additional liquidity.

Author: pringles1901
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: The functionality of the DEEX EXCHANGE launched on May, 25th, is constantly being improved. The first update was released almost immediately after the start, and we are ready to present you another major update, which has been fixed a lot of bugs and added some great features that significantly improve user interaction with the exchange.  So, here is the list of changes and fixes implemented in the updated version of alpha.deex.exchange: 1. New users receive 0.1 deex after the registration. 2. Night theme added. 3. Improved interface of the information panel (dashboard), in which "Deposit" and "Withdrawal" buttons was added. 4. Improved layout for Firefox browser. 5. Increased stability of the exchange, eliminated interface freezes while switching between markets and screens. 6. The option to select/view the balance in the desired currency with a convenient switch. 7. Improved the calendar to specify the expiration time of the order. 8. Improved design and layout elements. 9. The system login/logout and control of the user session. 10. Fixed issues with withdraw/deposit window, that now became more convenient for copy data from these windows. 11. Adaptation of the trading page (exchange) for wide screens monitors (aka "rubber layout"). 12. The interface of the information (dashboard) panel displays the login of your currently active account.  We are sure, you will appreciate these innovations. And remind you that we are also waiting for your feedback about the new release. Very soon we will present our new beta-version of the exchange, so stay in touch and follow DEEX' social networks and blogs. Body: Dear friends and partners!  We are happy to anounce the expansion of trading functionality of DEEX exchange. The number of assets available for trading has been replenished with several new tokens.  The first is the token of SteX cryptocurrency exchange (https://stex.exchange/), cooperation with which we have previously anounced. Mutual listing between DEEX and SteX will allow traders of both platforms to use deex and STE tokens for operations. The deex token is the main asset of the DEEX cryptocurrency ecosystem and allows its holders not only to trade in pairs with popular cryptocurrencies, but also to get profit from ownership. A2A (Any-2-Any) technology used in the operation of the SteX token exchange, allows you to trade any cryptocurrency from the list of TOP-100 and exchange any assets with a single action. Placing the deex token on the SteX platform will increase liquidity and trading volumes, which will have a positive impact on the value of the asset.  Another token, which was listed on the DEEX exchange, has become the token of the Ice Rock Mining project (https://icerockmining.io), offering users to earn on the mining of cryptocurrencies. The project allows owners of this token to obtain a steady income with transparent system of distribution of profit between holders of the asset.  In the near future we plan to increase the number of cryptocurrencies available for trading.

Body: Dear friends and partners!  Today we are pleased to announce the luanch of a new gateway to replenish exchange accounts using EOS. Despite the relative youth (EOS sales started in June 2017), this cryptocurrency is included in TOP-10 of the most valuable digital assets in terms of market' capitalization. Much of the credit for this rapid success belongs to the "godfather" of EOS - Dan Larimer, developer and inspirer of the Steemit social network and Bitshares platform. This is the world's first fully decentralized lottery platform built on Ethereum, managed by smart contracts without any human intervention. The lottery prize funds exceed 1200 ETH, and the FLOT tokens allow holders to receive a 10% commission from ticket sales and to play in lotteries as well. The Firelotto token will not only be traded on the exchange. The project and its technological developments will also be integrated into the DEEX ecosystem. Author: pringles1901
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: Dear friends and partners!  We have some news to publish for our bitcointalk community.  First is that Deex has almost completeted testing the gateways for in/out crypto. And we are happy to announce that we have already opened the withdraw for the first digital asset: ETH.  We carefully checked the correctness of the system, nevertheless we ask you to test the functioning of the gateway with small transfers before making large transactions. In the near future withdraw options for other cryptocurrencies and tokens will be done.  Together with the withdraw for ETH, the replenishment restrictions for the other gateways are removed. We are confident that this will allow you to more efficiently use the functionality of the Deex Exchange alpha-version.  We wish you all only successful trading and announce that in the very near future we will make several important announcements related to the development of the project of the main decentralized DEEX ecosystem.  Second is that on June 20th, in Tbilisi, Georgia the Blockchain & Bitcoin Conference Georgia conference organized by Smile Expo was held. Georgia is one of the most attractive countries for developers of crypto projects, miners and specialists in the field of blockchain technologies. Loyalty of the government and the legislative base of this country allow crypto-entusiast to implement world-class projects without fear of being in the "grip" of state regulators.  The comparatively low cost of electricity in Georgia allows miners to efficiently extract valuable digital resources without fear of ruining their accounts for electricity. The guests of the conference were representatives of various companies from Russia, Belarus, Ukraine, USA, Turkey, Azerbaijan and other countries. Future of blokchain technologies, cryptocurrency regulation and the legislative level, the presentation of new ICO: all these and much more topics has become the themes of speeches and discussions in the corridors of the hotel Radisson Blu Iveria Hotel, located in the heart of the ancient Tbilisi.  DEEX could not ignore this important for the whole industry event. Representatives of the main decentralized ecosystem were invited to Blockchain & Bitcoin Conference Georgia as a VIP guests. Despite the fact that this time there was no presentation, great speeches and reports, we were able to establish contacts with the leaders of the new promising projects, miners, developers and other participants. Negotiations were held with representatives of the Georgian "emoney.ge" payment systems, specialists of multifunctional project "glorymine", developers of "bixtrim" system, travelray.io and other promising projects who conducting ICO or just preparing for it. Among them is a promising "keepmycoin" project, working in the field of marketing with major global brands.  The third anouncement As you know, the DEEX' road map provides the creation of a secure decentralized messenger with financial functionality and integration into the DEEX Exchange engine. The first alpha-version of this product is scheduled for launch in middle of August. At the first stage of the project development, it is planned to create a company DEEX messenger based on the CrypViser partner technology engine.  Recently, the exchange functionality of the alpha version of Deex Exchange replenished with the trading pair with this trading asset. Bidding is presented in a pair of DEEX / CVCOIN, a link to the auction:  https://alpha.deex.exchange/market/CVCOIN_DEEX  Cooperation with the Crypviser platform, a decentralized messenger Deex is being created, which will provide users with an unprecedented level of communication security, video calling and working with crypto-currency wallets.  Owners of CVCOIN tokens can use them while making exchange transactions on the Deex exchange.   You can always stay in touch with our latest news via our official social networks and blogs  Telegram chat DEEX (eng) https://t.me/deexexchange DEEX blog: https://deex.blog/ DEEX channel https://t.me/deex_exchange_ru Facebook group https://www.facebook.com/groups/deex.exchange/ "Golos" blog https://golos.io/@deexexchange VKontakte group https://vk.com/deex.exchange Instagram https://www.instagram.com/the_deex/ Twitter page https://twitter.com/deex_exchange Blog on the Steemit project https://steemit.com/@deex Blog on the Medium project https://medium.com/@the_deex YouTube Page https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5oYUk9QC4kbM5ZBpodOUcQ

Author: pringles1901
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: Dear friends and partners! We are pleased to announce that we are opening a DEEX faucet and launching a lottery with prizes for all participants in the decentralized DEEX ecosystem. The faucet that issues tokens is available for new users, as well as for those who already have an account in the DEEX system. To receive a reward of 0.10 DEEX tokens, you must register a new account or use the existing one. What is this needs for? As you know, the DEEX token is a settlement unit of the decentralized DEEX ecosystem. In particular, the exchange commissions are paid with this token. As a consequence, this is a good way to attract new users, as well as a free option to receive funds for payment of exchange commissions by existing ones.  The DEEX faucet works at https://deex4free.com  The DEEX lottery is a great way to get an additional tokens by betting and guessing the token's rate. The results are processed automatically using a random number generator, so everyone can win, most importantly is the correct forecast and a little of luck. The lottery page is located at https://loto.deex.exchange/  Detailed rules can be found at https://loto.deex.exchange/rules In the future the lottery will transform into a full-fledged "prediction market", through which it will be possible to hedge its open positions on the cryptocurrency market.

Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY

Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: DEEX team is glad to inform you about the latest actual status of work on the DEEX project. The development team completes the work on the gateways for the main crypto currencies, builds the server infrastructure. Also the work on the corporate style and usability of the project is in progress.  As a part of the functionality implementation of the decentralized financial DEEX ecosystem, the project developers continue to realize useful tools that will form the basis for building a highly efficient crypto exchange platform. As we reported earlier, the DEEX system will include a decentralized messenger and a place for ICO conduction. The first step in the implementation of these tasks is deex.chat (https://deex.chat) - a message aggregator that use the most popular instant messengers.  It's an important tool for comunication between members of the DEEX ecosystem. It still has to become a single point of entry into the DEEX system and now you can evaluate the convenience of a universal solution for communicating through habitual messengers and social networks. Come on deex.chat and communicate in the familiar environment. Questions about the functioning and operation of the project can be asked through the Viber and Telegram messengers, as well as using authorization from social networks VK, Odnoklassniki, Facebook, Twitter and Instagram. The number of available entry points will be expanded and supplemented.  The actions of the supervisory authorities regarding the functioning of the most popular Telegram messenger, as we see, have already led to a deterioration of communications in the crypto community environment. That's why the issue of creating a decentralized messenger now is more relevant than ever. That is why our own decentralized messenger will soon release.  We also draw your attention to the fact that the technical support of DEEX moves to the ticketing system and will operate through the technical tasks portal https://deexhelp.zendesk.com. Requests are accepted from users of the system and after processing and solving the existing technical problem you will receive an appropriate notification with the status of the current issue and comments of a technical specialist.  Such a system will allow us to solve the incoming questions more quickly and with higher quality. You can be sure that no request will be left without attention. With the launch of the this processing system the Telegram chat https://t.me/deexbug (@deexbug) will stop working and technical issues will not be considered through this channel.  Please, follow our official accounts on the most popular social networks and blogs to stay updated with news regarding the latest steps of development.

Author: PG_deex
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: On February 21st, 2018, in Geneva, representatives of the main decentralized DEEX ecosystem took part in Blockchain & Bitcoin Conference Switzerland. DEEX is the general sponsor and partner of a series of international conferences dedicated to the development of blockchain and cryptocurrency technologies. The event was attended by industry leaders, developers of promising start-ups and already successfully implemented projects.  With the DEEX assistance, representatives of Blockchain Projects BV - the CEO of the company, Mrs. Annemieke Dirkes, as well as CTO of the company - Doctor of Technical Sciences, Mr. Fabian Schuh - performed on the same stage together with DEEX CEO - Vladislav Sapozhnikov. Blockchain Projects BV is the principal and sole executor of the assignments and tasks of the Bitshares Blockchain Foundation, which is the foundation and basis of the entire BitShares community. http://www.blockchainprojectsbv.com/  The joint presentation was a partnership of the parties, which opens great prospects for all those who involved in the development and promotion of the BitShares blockchain ecosystem.  "Partnership with Blockchain Projects BV is an important stage in the development of DEEX and we are confident that the technical knowledge, connections and impeccable reputation of our partners, coupled with the organizational capabilities and potential of DEEX, will give strong impulse to the powerful development of the whole BitShares community and increase interest of the audience and expansion of the users base, "- said after the conference DEEX CEO - Vladislav Sapozhnikov.  The (Stichting) BitShares Blockchain Foundation is a non-profit organization registered in Deventer, Netherlands. It is operational since June 2016 and has been preparing industries behind the scenes ever since. The Foundation's mission is to promote, advocate and grow the BitShares ecosystem to its full potential. http://www.bitshares.foundation/

Author: evg1394
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: March 6th, 2018 DEEX team participated in the Smile-Expo’s Blockchain conference in the heart of Thailand, in Bangkok. This event was among the series of international blockchain conferences, where DEEX acts as the main sponsor.  For the city to attain status of crypto capital there are still issues that have to be overcome. One of the matters that were shared by all the projects presented is fiat gateway. Also a major problem in Thailand as not long ago bank account of TDAX (Thai Digital Asset Exchange) in Bangkok Bank was terminated and the negative sentiment from government persists. Furthermore, the trust issue was one of the most frequently raised topics, due to the influx of maliciously intended projects in crypto community and nearly 42% of ICO’s not being able to finalize their aims in 2017.  The DEEX team being the main sponsor of the conference confidently faced the issues showing the solutions in the fast-changing Blockchain world. As a surprise to the guests and speakers of the event, we showed our revolutionary DEEX mobile app, that allows user in real time transfer tokens between Bitshares wallets in couple of seconds. We gifted to the most active guests newly made wallets with Bitshares coins on them. As a front development team in the Bitshares community (DEEX attained Bitshares Accreditation in February), we feel obliged to propagate not just our project, but the new future that is possible with the revolutionary Bitshares Blockchain. Everybody was astonished by the swift transaction operations possibility through the app. Moreover, DEEX application is integrated with investor dashboard of DEEX ICO ecosystem, so investors are able to gain access to their accounts via this application.  At the conference we have met new potential investors, traders and partners for DEEX ecosystem. For example, we have established business connections with the developers of stable coin on the Ethereum blockchain, which is asset backed by fiat currency - Thailand bat. DEEX soon will list this stable coin on our exchange, such that investors will gain access to reliable way of keeping their savings in stable currency in times of cryptocurrency storm. Moreover, some conference participants found out interest in developing the network of self-service crypto ATMs, produced by the DEEX. So, soon this ATMs will appear in some areas in Bangkok, as well as at the popular resorts.  The DEEX community is surprised by the fact that crypto conferences attract not just computer geeks and enthusiasts, but people from financial world of authoritarian countries, where demand is not satisfied by the governmentally regulated supply through severe restrictions. Moreover, the help and the will of the financiers to deliver decentralization with DEEX in those problematic regions also their way of making impossible possible are astonishing. Furthermore, DEEX’ prerogative is to help people, that is why we cannot leave other projects in dead-end created by regulations and always stretch out our helping hand to the ICO’s in early development or developed project in need of functionality of our platform, thus be prepared for the new partnerships on the way. Author: evg1394
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: Dear friends!  DEEX continues the road show and on Friday, December 8th will participate in CryproSpace blockchain conference in Skolkovo (Moscow Region, Russia). Under the curtain of the outgoing 2017 in the technological capital of Russia will take place an event which scale is impossible to overestimate. On December 8th the doors of the campus of the school of management of the Skolkovo Innovation Center will be opened for everyone who is interested in blockchain and who moves this technology forward. How and why to implement the blockchain? Why ICO became the hottest business topic in the outgoing year? Can we make money on cryptotrading in 2018? These and many other questions will be answered by the speakers of the event, who are counted as the leading crypto businessmen and authoritative opinion leaders in America, Asia and Europe. Most of them will come to Russia for the first time, which is an additional incentive for visiting CryptoSpace. The team of developers of the main decentralized cryptocurrency ecosystem DEEX will also take a direct part in the conference.  We will hold a presentation of the system, share plans for the future, tell about prospects for business development and submit the MVP. DEEX will have a separate booth and also will deliver a report. You will be able to personally communicate with the representatives of DEEX and learn how with the help of the latest technologies and unique functionality it is planned to conquer the tops of the blockchain by the project which only on the presale stage was able to collect investments worth more than $ 1,500,000.  Representatives of DEEX are regular participants of such events, this has already become a good tradition for the creators of the project. Most recently we successfully presented a decentralized ecosystem within the Blockchain & Bitcoin Conference 2017. You can see the detailed report of the event here https://www.facebook.com/groups/deex.exchange/permalink/130590004294872/ See you in Skolkovo! CryproSpace official site - http://cryptospace.moscow  Stay with us and follow us in popular blogs and social networks: DEEX telegram chat EN - https://t.me/deexexchange DEEX telegram channel RU - https://t.me/deex_exchange_ru Facebook group - https://www.facebook.com/groups/deex.exchange/ Golos blog - https://golos.io/@deexexchange VK group - https://vk.com/deex.exchange Instagram page - https://www.instagram.com/the_deex/ Twitter blog - https://twitter.com/deex_exchange Steemit blog - https://steemit.com/@deex Medium blog - https://medium.com/@the_deex Youtube channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5oYUk9QC4kbM5ZBpodOUcQ

Author: evg1394
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: The spread of the blockchain and cryptocurrencies as technologies that can change the interaction in the spheres of economic and financial relations is proceeding with leaps and bounds. And our country is on the first positions in terms of number blockchain projects and it certainly belongs to the number of leading countries that move this technology forward. Extra proof of this fact was the CryptoSpace conference, which took place on December 8th at the campus of the IT capital of Russia, the innovative center of Skolkovo.  Organizers of this event not only successfully chose its venue, but also attracted speakers from Russia, US and Europe. The scope of the conference was added not only by numerous sponsors, but also by a large number of journalists from the leading cryptocurrency and blockchain media. Representatives of DEEX https://deex.exchange  also became participants of the conference in Skolkovo, where they not only talked about the project of the main decentralized financial ecosystem, but also for the first time presented a working MVP prototype that had been developed over the past few months.  Familiarity with the working prototype attracted interest of both ordinary visitors and representatives of other blockchain projects. Everyone without exception could appreciate the scale of the DEEX project in terms of its direct functioning. It is not for nothing that it is said that it is better to see once than hear a hundred times. Direct acquaintance with MVP was very important for potential investors and developers of other block-based solutions. It turned out that visitors from different regions of Russia are aware of the DEEX project, and many have already invested their money in the token of the completed presale. Genuine interest in DEEX was shown by representatives of foreign countries from the Middle East, Asia, Europe, Canada, as well as large US funds offering cooperation. Representatives of other projects also made a number of interesting proposals on the mutual implementation and integration of promising solutions.  At the DEEX booth everyone (and there were many of them indeed) could personally try out terminals for accepting payments in cryptocurrencies and assess their convenience and simplicity. Exactly the same devices DEEX has recently presented at the exhibition Bitcoin & Blockchain conference 2017, a report from which you can see here https://www.facebook.com/groups/deex.exchange/permalink/130590004294872/  For the time since the presale of tokens (remember, it was held from October 26th till November 27th and was able to attract more than 3400Eth investments), many CryptoSpace visitors could already familiarize themselves with the project in detail and become its investors. Therefore, for them the conference became an excellent occasion to get acquainted personally with developers and creators of DEEX.  Speeches of the speakers aroused great interest, since the questions they are being asked about now are being asked by crypto-enthusiasts around the world. What will be the bitcoin course, what will it be possible to earn in 2018, what else can a blockchain as a technology...  We can say only one thing - the future belongs to decentralized systems and DEEX is by far the main platform for convenient cryptocurrency trading and ICO. Everyone who came to the conference in Skolkovo agreed to this. We suggest you to visit the website of the organizers http://cryptospace.moscow  in order to once again make sure that the future is closer than you think and the decentralized blockchain is its main driving force. Author: pringles1901
Title: DEEX EXCHANGE [ANN]+BOUNTY
Body: EXCHANGE & TRADING | SECURE FINANCIAL MESSENGER | CRYPTO FUND | ICO PLATFORM  DEEX is a trading platform of a new generation with the key idea of combining the best innovative solutions for modern cryptocurrency exchanges. After the successful implementation DEEX will transform to a global decentralized ecosystem. DEEX functionality based on the most modern blockchain platform Bitshares 2.0 (Graphene). By the first time DEEX will use the ready-made engine of the Bitshares exchange. The second stage of the project development is connected with the creation of its own engine for DEEX on the Graphene platform with its own nodes and a global cryptocurrency (token) similar to BTS.   A platform for safe ICO conduct in conjunction with the decentralized escrow toolkit from descrow.org. DEEX will be used as a platform for prospective project’s ICO, our specialists will carry out full project analysis, help them to receive funding from a permanent pool of private investors and further conduct pre-ICO and large-scale ICO. DEEX tokens investors will receive a share of revenues from all ICOs A platform for creating a decentralized transparent blockchain system for cryptofund managed by DEEX professional traders and issuing an appropriate stock token with automatic placement on both all DEX-Exchanges and leading centralized cryptocurrency Exchanges Cryptocurrency debit cards linked to users' wallets on DEEX and integration into fiat gateways, allowing to convert cryptocurrency into fiat when paid by card in outlets API for the integration of third-party applications and services with the DEEX platform Creation of the own agent network of crypto ATMs for the purchase and sale of cryptocurrency for fiat money with the ability to work with bank cards   WHITE PAPER DOWNLOAD https://deex.exchange/DEEX_wp_eng.pdf    https://predico.deex.exchange   On 26th of October 2017 the presale of DEEX tokens has started. During the presale we plan to raise funds in the amount of around $ 3,000,000 which then will be spent for DEEX cryptocurrency exchange prototype MVP development, marketing and advertisment campaign for ICO. The token price is - 0.10USD   You can join the PRESALE via this link:  http://presale-deex.exchange/signup  During the PRESALE campaign the discounts for investors will be the following •   25% for the first 10 days; •   20% from 11 to 15 days; •   15% from 16 to 20 days; •   10% from 21 to 23 days; •   5% from 24 to 26 days; •   0% from 27 to 30 days;    We believe in a decentralised economy and cryptocurrency community. Thats why we are starting a Bounty campaign, so participants can help us to tell about DEEX Exchange platform to the community and get free coins as a bounty reward. In the DEEX ICO there will be 100 000 000 coins issued in total. As a bounty reward we will distribute 3% (3 000 000) of total amount issued in ICO.  Calculation of payments from remuneration is made automatically by the system.  You can register in the project only by the referral link. To participate in the project's bounty campaign, send an e-mail to the following address: bounty@deex.exchange.  In the e-mail's body include your employer's referral link (line of code), for example:   FE2491518F4C758241465C75540D07E6DDA4E5DDC57E53DAB8C78B9916EB567A  Each member of the bounty receives 10% of Deex tokens from revenues, all employees involved. The total income of the project participant is accumulated from 90% of the revenue for the work done and 90% of the income from referral links. 10% of income for the work done and 10% of income from referral links goes to the employer.  TWITTER & FACEBOOK CAMPAIGNS   Conditions  User need to follow our official Twitter and Facebook pages https://twitter.com/deex_exchange | https://www.facebook.com/groups/deex.exchange/  Retweet and repost news marked with #deex from our official account within 7 days after their publication and not later, and do not delete them for 20 days. Each retweet and repost will earn the following amount of tokens:  •   29 followers and less - 1 token; •   From 30 to 99 followers - 3 tokens; •   From 100 to 249 followers - 5 tokens; •   From 250 to 999 followers - 10 tokens; •   From 1000 to 9999 followers - 20 tokens; •   10000 followers and more - 50 tokens.  The account must be at least 5 months old. The number of the followers is being fixed at the moment when users connect their accounts and doesn’t change during the campaign.  NOTE: We count ONLY the posts that are marked with #deex by our official team. So, if user add our hashtag to any other posts, it is not counted.  Bitcointalk Signature Campaign We are glad to invite users to the DEEX Bitcointalk signature campaign. All need is to receive the signature and avatar provided by us and write at least one constructive post within 3 days.  Each week completed will earn you the following amount of tokens: Legendary/Hero: 20 tokens; Sr./Full: 15 tokens; Member: 10 tokens; Jr. Member: 5 tokens; Avatar on: +5 tokens. Conditions to earn reward in this category: •   Constructive posts in a 3 days minimum; •   At least 1 post a week must be constructive and in the DEEX thread; •   As you apply, we define your rank, and it will not be changed; •   To get signature rewards, you need at least 20 posts written; •   We will ban and will not send coins to spammers and multi accounts; •   We don’t reward avatars, only as an addition to signatures; •   Users not posting posts per week will be removed; •   Receiving negative trust or ban during your participation in our campaign will result in you being disqualified from our campaign receiving nothing.  Signature for bounty users can be found here https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2375913.msg25853075#msg25853075  Avatars:      NOTE: If we feel there's a lot of spam posts you're making you will be removed from the campaign and receive no payment. Do not change signature during campaign.  Discussion Boards we do not count: Games and round, Micro earnings, Politics and Society, Off-topic, Archival, Auctions, Lending, Beginners and help, Press.   If you want to participate in our Bitcointalk signature campaign, please write us via this Telegram chat https://t.me/deex_bounty   As the part of Bounty Campaign you can earn reward for making translation and publishings. We will be glad to work with popular cryptocurrency and blockchain authors who can tell the world about DEEX. If you can tell about DEEX through your blog, magazine or youtube channel - just write us about yourself and show what you can do.  The volume of the article must be at least 1000 characters. Placement of personal text is possible in any of the social networks available to the user, as well as in personal blogs or on profile resources. Depending on the quality of the material, the number of friends or readers, the number of tokens received by the author will vary as follows:   Standard (from 200 to 500 tokens);  good (from 400 to 700 tokens);  excellent (from 500 to 1000 tokens).    If you can help us to translate DEEX materials into one of the European or Asian languages - you're welcome too! You reward will be counted individually.  Please, feel free to ask your questions in https://t.me/deex_bounty   You can also join our popular social accounts https://t.me/deexexchange https://www.facebook.com/groups/deex.exchange/ https://vk.com/deex.exchange https://www.instagram.com/the_deex/ https://twitter.com/deex_exchange https://www.reddit.com/user/the_deex https://github.com/thedeex https://golos.io/@deexexchange https://steemit.com/@deex https://medium.com/@the_deex https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5oYUk9QC4kbM5ZBpodOUcQ
